        "Title": "Article: Black Workers Evaluated More Harshly",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClass2E91F6D593C040B286937330E28F314E\"><p>Check out this article&#58; &#160;<a href=\"http&#58;//www.citylab.com/work/2015/10/black-workers-really-do-need-to-be-twice-as-good/409423/\">http&#58;//www.citylab.com/work/2015/10/black-workers-really-do-need-to-be-twice-as-good/409423/</a></p><p>A recent study concluded that Black workers are evaluated more harshly then their white counterparts. &#160;The outcome is a cycle that lead to more time unemployed between jobs and, accordingly, less economic advancement in the work world.</p><p>More evidence of the intersection between race and poverty.</p><p><br></p></div>",
