        "Title": "Getting Out Our Story: LAF and the Media",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClass54458EB89D624E29870E9B17449A5FDC\"><p><span style=\"color&#58;rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Yesterday, Karianna Simpkins and Rich Wheelock delivered the training &quot;Getting Out Our Story&#58; LAF and the Media.&quot; The <a href=\"https&#58;//my.lafpoint.lafchicago.org/personal/wheelock/_layouts/15/start.aspx#/Documents/Forms/All.aspx?RootFolder=/personal/wheelock/Documents/Press%20Training%20Packet&amp;FolderCTID=0x0120005A9F1D4DEE48684FADA98FF75EC1F3EB&amp;View=%7b84F48055-DD40-47F6-8072-E426DFFF4B62%7d\">Press Training Packet&#160;</a>is now located (on an interim basis) as a folder in Rich's&#160;OneDrive or you can click <a href=\"https&#58;//my.lafpoint.lafchicago.org/personal/wheelock/_layouts/15/start.aspx#/Documents/Forms/All.aspx?RootFolder=/personal/wheelock/Documents/Press%20Training%20Packet&amp;FolderCTID=0x0120005A9F1D4DEE48684FADA98FF75EC1F3EB&amp;View=%7b84F48055-DD40-47F6-8072-E426DFFF4B62%7d\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.&#160; Getting&#160;our stories&#160;out to the public can make a real difference for our clients, our client communities, and LAF (in terms of attracting donors and pro bono help and establishing our reputation locally and nationally).&#160; Please take a moment to browse the documents contained in the packet.&#160; In particular, please review the LAF Public Relations Protocol.&#160; The Press Training Packet folder also contains a press release template, media contacts, Do’s and Don’ts of Interacting with the Media, and much much&#160;more.&#160; </span></p></div>",
