        "Title": "Transgender Film Project Seeks Kickstart",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClass164CFDA7788B417C8384B6D8AB7D098D\"><p>A friend of mine has been working for several years on a film documenting the lives of transgendered individuals in the tech industry.&#160; He is now launching a Kickstarter campaign to fund the final phase of production.&#160; Please consider supporting this project which promotes understanding - the first step toward promoting civil rights.&#160; You can read about Kevin's project here&#58;</p><p><a href=\"https&#58;//www.kickstarter.com/projects/transgeekmovie/trans-geek-movie-gender-identity-and-geek-culture\">https&#58;//www.kickstarter.com/projects/transgeekmovie/trans-geek-movie-gender-identity-and-geek-culture</a></p><p>-Dan Lindsey<br></p><p><br></p></div>",
