        "Title": "Small Claims Workshop at Truman College",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClassC3A9743560714035810A4D8F95F8B192\"><p style=\"text-align&#58;left;\">Jim Brady and I&#160;led a Small Claims workshop at Truman College.&#160;&#160; We were joined by Marko Stojkovic, a Consumer Law Fellow at Loyola School of Law (featured on the far left). Participants were able to identify the type of cases that can be brought in small claims court, describe the process of bringing a case in small claims court and simulate a small claims trial.&#160;&#160; </p><p style=\"text-align&#58;left;\">Thanks to Jim and Marko for sharing their legal knowledge with the students.<br></p><p>&#160;</p><p style=\"text-align&#58;center;\">&#160;</p></div>",
