        "Title": "Celebrating Volunteers - Stan Birnbaum",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClassA8A4918CA4534C8DA7E9927505B41175\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;text-align&#58;left;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">Before Stan came to LAF, he'd spent</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">&#160;35 years working for the Social Security Administration doing everything from claims authorizations to disability.</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">&#160;&#160;It shouldn't come as a surprise to anyone who's worked in public benefits to hear that Stan was never short on cases at the Social Security Administration and the work was never boring. &#160;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">This made the transition to LAF easy.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;background-color&#58;transparent;\">&#160;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;text-align&#58;left;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">Since 2011, Stan has volunteer</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">ed</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&#160;</span>about two days a week doing document reviews for disability decisions.&#160; He is more than happy to take on any projects we throw his way, and he’s an extremely valuable asset for our entire organization.&#160; He also acts as an incredib</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">le&#160;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">resource to our public benefits staff.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCX146506134\">&#160;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;text-align&#58;left;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">Originally from Washington DC, Stan moved to Chicago in 1964 to be closer to family.&#160; He currently lives in Oak Park with his wife who practices private therapy.&#160; They have two children, and three grandchildren, who they get to see every other week.&#160; When he’s not spending time with his family or reviewing documents at LAF, he’s getting his hands dirty volunteering every Saturday at the Garfield Park Conservatory.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCX146506134\">&#160;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;text-align&#58;left;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">This Pro Bono Week, and every other week too, please join us in thanking Stan for all the hard work he does at LAF.&#160; Our clients and staff are lucky to have him.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCX146506134\">&#160;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCX146506134\" style=\"color&#58;windowtext;text-align&#58;left;background-color&#58;transparent;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCX146506134\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCX146506134\" style=\"background-color&#58;inherit;\">We are extremely grateful for the service you provide and thank you from the bottom of our hearts.</span></span></p></div></div>",
