        "ContentTypeId": "0x0110002675B935B1E1CA40903215A1EC22F4C4",
        "Title": "A Friendly Face - A Beautiful Message",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClassA94D83D758814A749E30404440D8526F\"><p><a href=\"https&#58;//www.youtube.com/watch?v=TYednQjJjAg\">https&#58;//www.youtube.com/watch?v=TYednQjJjAg</a></p><p>I passed Daniel every single day on the way to work and from work and I never bothered to stop to say hello. &#160;Next time I see him, I'll make sure to wish him a good day back.</p></div>",
        "NumCommentsId": 0,
