        "Title": "Lilian Lands Long-shot Loan Mod",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClassBFA69B99E67B431E926C08EDB2CF926B\"><p>Kudos to CPG Paralegal Lilian Lepe for landing her first loan mod, made all the more challenging because our client had to get title from her spouse in the middle of a divorce.&#160; Indeed, it is the first case we know of where we got a loan mod for a divorcing spouse before the Judgment of Dissolution was entered.&#160; Lilian and I worked this case with assistance from Benna Crawford and Suzy Stockton, so this was also an example of nice inter-group interface.&#160; Great work, great result&#58; foreclosure avoided, home saved.<br></p></div>",
