        "Title": "LAF Trivia masters win big!",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClass1ADA928426E4476F81DD942F8993C3FA\"><p>On Tuesday night, the CBF hosted a trivia night at Revolution Brewing for Pro Bono Week. LAF's team (Dan Kresse, Mischa Fleishman, Kevin Zickterman, Michelle Gilbert, Aidan Gilbert (Michelle's husband), and Kate Shank) tied for first place (with Chicago Coalition for the Homeless), and took home $1,000 for LAF! Their knowledge of Justin Beiber's criminal record, the Law and Order series, and what the heck the CARPLS acronym stands for helped them bring home the big money.&#160;</p></div>",
