        "Title": "VISTAs Make Kids Smile",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClass124CD1FB04E2404A82CD0DC8556DC736\"><p><font color=\"#646464\">Last Friday, LAF VISTAs took part in a Day of Service, which saw us throwing Halloween parties for kids currently assisted by the Primo Center for Women and Children, a transitional housing provider. As one could imagine, the event was quite a hit, and we brought smiles to so many faces. </font></p><p><font color=\"#646464\">When VISTAs leave the office and head out into the community with a mission, great things happen. The Primo Center staff could not have been happier to work with us and were incredibly thankful for our donation of time and resources.&#160;Congrats to my fellow VISTAs for making our Day of Service such a huge success. </font></p></div>",
