        "Title": "LAFPoint Q&As Every Month",
        "Body": "<div class=\"ExternalClassF8A0D66C54E04CA1817039B4081932F0\"><p>The LAFPoint Q&amp;A sessions we held in October worked well so we plan to continue these sessions on a monthly basis. Monthly Q&amp;A sessions will take place on the first Thursday of every month from 11&#58;00 a.m. - 12&#58;00 p.m. in Room 1078 starting today, November 5. Please bring your questions, comments, and ideas about using LAFPoint. Hope to see you there!</p></div>",
